<section>
    <h2>RStudio Project (3/3)</h2>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="left">
            <ul>
                <li>
                    Directory Name: <code>foo</code>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <code>~</code> is your home directory
                </li>
                <li>
                    If you don't know what git is, don't start a
                    repository.<br /><br />
                    If you do, RStudio will instantiate an empty git
                    repo at the project root.
                </li>
                <li>
                    If you open in a new session, RStudio will open a new window.
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="right">
            <img src="{{site.baseurl}}/public/img/rstudio-new-project-3.png" alt="RStudio: New Project" width="100%">
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

